# reference/repos/ — local clones of external library source used as ground
# truth for the agent's grep-before-code workflow. NEVER commit the cloned
# source — it bloats the repo, blows out CI checkout time, and the canonical
# copies are upstream anyway. We commit only the README + setup script that
# tells future agents how to reconstruct the folder.

# Ignore everything in this directory ...
*

# ... except the metadata files that describe what should be here.
!.gitignore
!README.md
!setup.sh
